OL,6,FAfter firing shots at the Showcase
OL,7,FCinema, he went to a Go Local store
OL,8,Fwhere he "bought two mini bottles of
OL,9,Fvodka on credit", before remaining in
OL,10,Fthe area of his mum's house on
OL,11,FTernhall Road for roughly an hour.
