OL,7,Fopened the door and was escorted from
OL,8,Fthe premises at gunpoint.JThe
OL,9,Fdefendant then presented at the
OL,10,Fentrance wearing a t-shirt and boxer
OL,11,Fshirts in an "agitated and aggressive"
OL,12,Fstate. When officers pointed their
OL,13,Fguns towards him, he replied: "F***
OL,14,Foff d***head."JGarrett was tasered and
OL,15,Ffell to the floor, at which point he
OL,16,Fwas handcuffed and arrested. He gave
